headline: Industrial sector outperformance: 3 themes to watch
summary: The industrial sector (XLI) has outperformed the S&P 500 (^GSPC) year to date. Neuberger Berman portfolio manager for climate innovation and next-generation space economy strategy, Evelyn Chow, outlines three themes to watch in the industrial sector. She also shares some top stock picks in the sector that are set to benefit from these themes.
